column1: yazidi_religion_desc0: "The eternal god created the universe and his seven angels. First among them is Melek Taus
column2: whom god gave stewardship of the world."

column1: yazidi_desc0: "The Yazidi believe that God created the world and placed it under the protection of seven angels
column3: the Peacock Angel. The Peacock Angel at first fell from God's grace
column4: but his tears of remorse extinguished the fires of his prison
column5: and he was reunited with God. In the same manner
column6: we all seek to reunite with God at the end of many long lifetimes."
